drm/i915: Kill has_dp_encoder from pipe_config

Use the new output_types bitmask instead of has_dp_encoder.
To make it less oainlful provide a small helper
(intel_crtc_has_dp_encoder()) to do the bitsy stuff.

v2: Rebase

